[gd_scene load_steps=13 format=3]

; Fixture: hermetic curved room
; Purpose: sealed six-receiver chamber for scene-contract hit closure validation.
; Contract: every camera ray is expected to hit one receiver wall unless traversal
; budget, integration instability, topology ambiguity, or an explicit valid
; exception prevents closure. V1 has no valid non-hit exception regions.

